@startuml
title Sequence Diagram — Status and Presentation

actor Client
participant Application
participant VideoService

Client -> Application : checkStatus(jobId)
Application -> VideoService : getStatus(jobId)
VideoService --> Application : status, progress
Application --> Client : show status

Client -> Application : downloadPresentation(jobId)
Application -> VideoService : getPresentation(jobId)
VideoService --> Application : presentation file
Application --> Client : return presentation
@enduml